<p><strong>Show notes for Mac Geek Gab Podcast For July 14, 2008</strong></p>
<p>MobileMe&#39;s out, so Dave and John will discuss what&#39;s different (and what&#39;s the same). Plus it&#39;s summer season in the USA, and that means thunderstorms for a lot of folks, so protecting yourself against lightening is another topic. Listener questions and tips round out the show and, oh yeah, Dave went and got an iPhone 3G, so he talks about that, too!</p>
